<div class="container">
    <h1>About Canara Bank</h1>
    <p>
        <strong>Canara Bank</strong> is one of the oldest and most respected public sector banks in India. 
        It was established in 1906 in Mangalore and later nationalized in 1969. Over the years, the bank 
        has grown into a major financial institution, offering a wide range of services such as retail banking, 
        corporate banking, digital banking, and financial inclusion services.
    </p>
    <p>
        Canara Bank is known for its customer-centric approach, innovation in banking technology, and commitment 
        to social welfare. With a vast network of branches and ATMs across India and overseas, it serves millions 
        of customers and businesses with integrity and trust.
    </p>
    <p>
        In recent years, Canara Bank has focused on digitizing its services, providing customers with 
        internet banking, mobile banking apps, and robust cybersecurity features to ensure safe and efficient banking.
    </p>
    <p>
        <strong>Motto:</strong> "Together We Can"
    </p>
